{"tid":1564384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歌係其中一種散播革命思想既方法","createTime":"2019-09-12T17:45:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T05:50:08.000Z","uid":254123,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"4801f2c945acbaf34b694f44dc74f0abadb83a06","tid":1564384,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:45:36.000Z","msg":"鑑於最近有一大堆post爭吵是否用榮光做國歌，或者驚變返做雨革嘉年華式既方向等等既風向，我認為有需要好好地討論下。<br />\n<br />\n我既結論就已經係標題打左。<br />\n<br />\n首先大家都應該聽過四面楚歌呢個成語，先唔討論<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">榮光</span></span> 係唔係國歌先，但一定係中共既 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">楚歌</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n18區每晚都奏起，甚至好多群眾都會自發性集合去唱歌，叫口號等等，對於中共黎講，實在同金剛圈既咒語冇分別。<br />\n<br />\n而且亦都激起左香港人自我意識，身分認同既萌芽。<br />\n<br />\n獨裁政權最害怕既就係市民奏起自由之歌，因為咁樣會令星星之火燒遍整個土地。<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻格硬要講港獨其實只係一個偽命題，只係中共扣帽子既手段。<br />\n<br />\n中共最驚既係，香港人會教識一堆被洗腦左咁多年既人咩叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自由</span>。<br />\n<br />\n當年唱今天我...同今日唱 榮光 既決定性唔同就係呢度。<br />\n<br />\n而且fight club教條頭兩條係咩我諗好多連登仔都懂的。<br />\n<br />\n而呢一首楚歌，亦係抗爭時都係一種好強既精神支持。<br />\n<br />\n所以，只係兄弟爬山既其中一個路線！<br />\n<br />\n時刻提醒自己，一日未爭取到五大訴求，每一次 我地都會企出黎。<br />\n<br />\n香港下一步唔需要急於係依家討論，到有左真普選，先係決定前路既時候。"},{"pid":"86b4390d41f54968d312fd2c2b860b2c2e8e7e32","tid":1564384,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:45:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"809c9b1d7822fdcd192d05e9d1e4dc9f164e4412","tid":1564384,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:51:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4oZup8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4oZup8.jpg&h=22278f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=fcc3a75b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=c97c8f94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"a4f528d5ceafebb99ff5de0f5b83cd3217db84fb","tid":1564384,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e5398fca18b0a11041ade4a1cec7c78975f69c","tid":1564384,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0407278ba58b6a402d2bb280b8815fd37c1430f","tid":1564384,"uid":262997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:56:32.000Z","msg":"希望大家睇下 唔好再互屌<br />\n<br />\n你地係咪要互屌到林鄭卸任先停呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1564391\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1564391</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1a83260704916e4b7d8b912156065d3348fe0317","tid":1564384,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bff22be8077bbcf4ba7